snippet.title: Custody Full Movie | 2023 New Released Hindi Dubbed Movie | Naga Chaitanya, Krithi Shetty, Priyamani
snippet.description:
Here's presenting "CUSTODY" the Hindi Dubbed Version of the Telugu action thriller Film "CUSTODY", starring Naga Chaitanya, Krithi Shetty, Priyamani, Arvind Swamy, Anandhi, R. Sarath Kumar, Jiiva and Sampath Raj in lead roles.    

Movie (Hindi Dubbed):- Custody 
Original Movie Name:- Custody in Telugu 
StarCast:- Naga Chaitanya, Krithi Shetty, Priyamani, Arvind Swamy, Jiiva, R. Sarath Kumar, Sampath Raj, Anandhi
Music:- Yuvan Shankar Raja, Ilaiyaraaja 
Producer:- Srinivasaa Chituri 
Director:- Venkat Prabhu 

Constable Shiva is assigned to escort a witness from police custody to the courtroom. However, he soon learns Shiva that the entire police department wants the witness dead.

snippet.title: Kapil Dev और MS Dhoni IND vs AUS Final मैच देखने क्यों नहीं गए, असली वजह तो ये थी | World Cup 2023
snippet.description:
रजिस्ट्रेशन लिंक: https://adda.thelallantop.com/?userId... 

Story Link:  https://www.thelallantop.com/sports/post/kapil-dev-not-invited-in-world-cup-2023-india-australiafinal-match-says-people-forget-sometimes   

In the final match of the ICC World Cup 2023, Australia defeated India by 6 wickets. Not only sports enthusiasts but also personalities from the realms of politics and arts gathered to witness the clash. However, notable figures like Kapil Dev, the captain of the 1983 World Cup-winning Indian team, and Mahendra Singh Dhoni, the captain of the 2011 World Cup-winning team, were conspicuously absent from any VIP boxes. What could be the reason behind their absence? Uncover the mystery in this video.

snippet.title: Visakha Harbour Fire Accident: యూట్యూబర్ లోకల్ బాయ్ నాని ప్రమేయం లేదన్న పోలీసులు.. అసలేం జరిగింది?
snippet.description:
విశాఖపట్నం ఫిషింగ్ హర్బర్ చరిత్రలో ఎన్నడూ లేని స్థాయిలో భారీ అగ్ని ప్రమాదం జరిగింది.  ఈ అగ్నిప్రమాదానికి సంబంధించి తాము అదుపులోకి తీసుకున్న యూట్యూబర్ నాని (లోకల్ బాయ్ నానీ)కి ఈ ఘటనలో ప్రమేయం లేదని పోలీసులు చెప్పారు.

నవంబరు 20న అదుపులోకి తీసుకున్న నానీని, ఈ ప్రమాదంలో అతడి పాత్ర లేదని తేలడంతో విడిచిపెట్టామని తెలిపారు.

హార్బర్ సమీపంలోని హెచ్‌పీసీఎల్ ట్యాంకర్ల వద్ద ఉన్న సీసీటీవీ ఫుటేజ్‌ను పరిశీలించామని, వీటి ఆధారంగా ఈ ప్రమాదానికీ, నానీకి ఎలాంటి సంబంధమూ లేదని విచారణలో తేల్చామని విశాఖపట్నం వన్ టౌన్ సీఐ భాస్కరరావు వివరించారు.

localized.title: Visakha Harbour Fire Accident: యూట్యూబర్ లోకల్ బాయ్ నాని ప్రమేయం లేదన్న పోలీసులు.. అసలేం జరిగింది?
localized.description:
విశాఖపట్నం ఫిషింగ్ హర్బర్ చరిత్రలో ఎన్నడూ లేని స్థాయిలో భారీ అగ్ని ప్రమాదం జరిగింది.  ఈ అగ్నిప్రమాదానికి సంబంధించి తాము అదుపులోకి తీసుకున్న యూట్యూబర్ నాని (లోకల్ బాయ్ నానీ)కి ఈ ఘటనలో ప్రమేయం లేదని పోలీసులు చెప్పారు.

నవంబరు 20న అదుపులోకి తీసుకున్న నానీని, ఈ ప్రమాదంలో అతడి పాత్ర లేదని తేలడంతో విడిచిపెట్టామని తెలిపారు.

హార్బర్ సమీపంలోని హెచ్‌పీసీఎల్ ట్యాంకర్ల వద్ద ఉన్న సీసీటీవీ ఫుటేజ్‌ను పరిశీలించామని, వీటి ఆధారంగా ఈ ప్రమాదానికీ, నానీకి ఎలాంటి సంబంధమూ లేదని విచారణలో తేల్చామని విశాఖపట్నం వన్ టౌన్ సీఐ భాస్కరరావు వివరించారు.
#VisakhaHarbourFireAccident #AndhraPradesh   #visakhapatnam #vizag 

___________

Episode 3932: Sundar Ka Waada
--------------------------------------------------------
Jethalal is concerned that Sundar is not fulfilling his word as he is not picking up his calls or answering text messages. To get Daya back, he arranges for Taarak and himself to travel to Ahmedabad. He visits Taarak's place who were planning to go shopping together. Jetha meets Bhide and Sodhi in the compound and asks the reason for his sadness to which he tells them about the uncooked plan of Daya's arrival. Watch the episode.

Episodes No - 3932, 18 Nov 2023

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:

Mannat Murad Episode 16 - [Eng Sub] - Iqra Aziz - Talha Chahour - Digitally Presented by PEL - 20th November 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Mannat Murad Digitally Presented by PEL

Mannat is a beautiful young girl who hails from a progressive family that values love, care, and mutual respect. Raised in an environment where everyone's choices are respected, Mannat enjoys the freedom to make her own decisions. Following the untimely demise of her parents, she finds support from her elder brother, Nafees, who showers her with affection.

On the other hand, Murad belongs to a conservative family where his mother, the matriarch, wields significant influence over his life choices. As the only son, Murad is burdened with the responsibility of fulfilling his family's expectations. Soft-spoken and romantic by nature, Murad finds himself unable to defy his mother's authority, especially after the passing of his father.

Despite their starkly contrasting backgrounds, Mannat and Murad's hearts find solace in each other's presence, and they fall deeply in love. However, their families' interference creates misunderstandings between Mannat and Murad, testing the strength of their bond.

Will their families agree to their union? Will Mannat's family, with their open-mindedness, find common ground with Murad's conservative household? Can Mannat and Murad's love for each other withstand the motives of their families, who seek to create further misunderstandings between them?

"Main Aur Main" by Kayden Sharma is an introspective rap that explores self-love, spiritual contemplation, and the pursuit of contentment. The lyrics touch on the challenges of societal expectations, advocate for embracing solitude, and reflect on personal growth and transformation.

Credits 
Track Name: Main Aur Main
Written & Performed By: @kaydensharma 
Music Produced By: @KaranKanchanYT  HMLYA 

Music Label: @tseries 

Genre: Hip Hop

Sub-Genre: Rap

Language: Hindi, English

Country Of Origin/Source: India

Mix and Mastered by: Hanish Taneja (Studio Alika)

Watch/Tune in to POCO MTV Hustle 03 Represent, Co-powered by Govo Soundbars, T-Series, Wildstone & Appy Fizz, Every Sat-Sun 7PM only on MTV & JioCinema

#MTVHustle03 #MTVHustle #Kayden 

Lyrics

JAB KAAM SE HO PYAAR TOH AATA PHIR INAAM KHUD SE
KAAM SE HOTA PYAAR  AGAR TU KARTA PYAAR KHUD SE
AB AATA SAWAAL KI KHUD SE KAISE HOTA PYAAR
ANTAR AATMA KI SUNN TAB HI HOTA PYAAR KHUD SE
BHEJA TERA GARAM KYON KI GLASS MEIN TERE BARAF
SACHAI SAMAJHNE MEIN TU LAGATA KITNE BARAS
KUCH LOG DETE ADVICE KI GO WITH THE FLOW
LEKIN AISA RASTA JAATA KHAALI NARAK KI TARAF
TERI MANZIL TERA RASTA  TERE SE ACHA KOI NAHI JAANTA
JAB TAK TU SAFAL NAHI  TERI SACHI BAAT BHI KOI NAHI MAANTA
BRAHM  JHOOTH  MURKHATA DIKHTI AB SRUSHTI MEIN DUNIYA JAGAANE CHALA WOH 
JO KHUD SUBAHE JALDI UTH NAHI PAATA
LOGO KI EK AADAT HAI CHASE KARNE KI
HAR DIN KISI NA KISI SE RACE KARNE KI
PAR YEH RACE NAHI HOGI KHATAM  AUR HUM BHAAGTE HI RAHENGE
AUR JEET KE BHI HARENGE YEH RACE HAI AISI
TOH HUM KYU PANA CHAHTE AISA SUKH  JO HAI DO SHAN KA
AISA SUKH PAANE K LIYE MURKH NAHI TOH KAUN LADTA 
JEEVAN KA MATLAB TOH JAANTA NAHI INSAAN 
BUS CHEHRA RAKHTA SAAF  PAR MAN MEIN RAKHTA BOHOT SHANKA
INDRIYO KO SANTUSHTI DENA BAND KAR
NARI AUR DHAN KO CHASE KARNA BAND KAR
SANTUSHT HI  KARNA HAI TOH AATMA KO KAR
AUR CHASE KARNA HAI TOH PARAM AATMA KO KAR
KYUKI JO HAI PARAM SATYA WOH KAISE DEGA DHOKA 
USME HUA VISHWAS JAB MAIN KARMO KA PHAL BHOGA
ZINDAGI MEIN LOGA WAIT  KARTE MOUKE KA PAR
KOI NAHI SAMAJHTA ZINDAGI KHUD HI EK MOUKA
JO HAI TOUFA UPAR WALE KA  JISKO MAIN HAR DIN KHOLTA
YOGI YA GYANI NAHI MAI BUS MIC KE SAMNE DIL KHOLTA
JITTE HOTE HUM LOGO KE  SARR PE BAAL TERA EK GALAT VICHAAR
UTNE LOG KE DIL TODTA

IF IT'S NOT A CLEAR YES  IT'S A CLEAR NO
PAR MANN HAMARA CHANCHAL ISLIYE SATYA KO PEHCHANTA NAHI
DO SAAL PEHLE JO THA MAIN USKO AGAR ADVICE DU TOH YAHI BOLUNGA KI TERE DHARAM SE DOOR JAANA NAHI
AAKHIR EK INSAAN HU KHUDA SE KYA LADUNGA
AAKHIR EK SHARIR HUN JALKE HI RAHUNGA
ZINDAGI MEIN SAB KUCH NAHI HAI MERE HAATH MEIN
LEKIN JO HAI MERE HATH MEIN WOH TOH KAR K HI MARUNGA

RISHTO KI MAANGTA KYUN BHEEKH
AKELE REHNA SEEKH JO SUNE NA TERI CHEEKH
KYA KAAM KA WOH RELATIONSHIP
BAATAA  MERI SIMPLE PAR LAGRI TEKO DEEP CUZ
YOU'RE VERY FAR AWAY FROM THE REALITY 
JAB MAIN BOLA TEKO KI AKELE REHNA SEEKH
YOU HAVE NO IDEA WHAT DOES IT ACTUALLY MEAN 
OKAY OKAY OKAY LET ME GUESS WHAT YOU  IMAGINING
BEING ALONE IN YOUR HOME AND SCROLLING YOUR FEED
GOING ON A SOLO TRIP PUTTING YOUR EARBUDS AND GET LOST IN THAT BEATS 

MATLAB INSAAN HO YA CHEEZ TEKO DONO KI HAI NEEDS EK BAAR PUCH KHUD SE PLEASE 
KYUN NAHI BAITH SAKTA TU SHANTI SE 5 MINUTE 
KYUN TEKO CHECK KARNA HAI PHONE KO HAR 5 MINUTE 
BOHOT BADA BUSINESSMEN HAI TU  24 GHANTE MEIN
KYUN NAHI NIKAL SAKTA TU KHUD KE LIYE 5 MINUTE
BEFORE WE CHEAT OTHERS WE CHEAT OURSELVES
AND BEING ALONE IS THE ONLY OPTION FOR GETTING FREE
AKELE REHNA TERI ICCHA PE NAHI HAI THAT'S THE ONLY WAY TO LIVE
ARE YOU GETTING ME

RISHTE BANTE TOOTNE KO KOI NAHI DETA SAATH
PAR TOOTNE KE BAAD MEIN ICH HOTA YE EHSAAS
JITTA WEAK THA MERA PAST  UTTA STRONG BANA MAIN AAJ
KARTA BUDDHI PE MEIN RAJ KYUKI BAN GAYA USKA DAS
SHARIRIK SUNDARTA MEIN AB LAGTA NAHI KUCH KHAAS
JO DHOONDA MAIN DUNIYA MEIN MEKU MILA MERE PASS
JANAM HUA MERA BOHOT FILMY TAREEKE SE
MARNE K SAMAY TOH RACHUNGA ITIHAAS HAAN

ICC Men's T20 World Cup 2024

The 2024 ICC Men's T20 World Cup is scheduled to be the 9th edition of the T20 World Cup, a biennial Twenty20 International (T20I) tournament contested by men's national teams and organised by International Cricket Council (ICC). It is scheduled to be hosted by the West Indies and the United States from 4 June to 30 June 2024.
It will be the first ICC World Cup tournament to feature matches played in the United States.

snippet.description:

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha

snippet.title: Highlights || Bhilwara Kings VS India Capitals || 1st Match || Legends League Cricket 2023
snippet.description:
Highlights || Bhilwara Kings VS India Capitals || 1st Match || Legends League Cricket 2023

#legendsleaguecricket2023  #LLCT20 #BossLogonKaGame



About : Legends League Cricket

Legends League Cricket is dedicated to cricket lovers and is a pioneer in offering a platform where retired cricket players can demonstrate their skills, engage with fans, and sense the thrill of cricket once again. The league is dedicated to bring cricket enthusiasts from all walks of life together to celebrate this exciting sport. 

At Legends League Cricket, there are two distinctive cricketing formats being played: Regional and Franchise. Each format gives the game its own charm and competitiveness, providing players and fans with a combination of exciting encounters. 

Legends League Cricket introduced its global format, LLC Masters in 2022 in an effort to push the limits of cricketing excellence. Its inaugural season was hosted by Muscat, Oman, and the most recent season was hosted by Doha, Qatar. The three teams that compete in this format to showcase the best of talent: Indian Maharajas, Asia Lions, and World Giants. Representing the nation’s cricket-crazy culture, India Maharajas bring together the best Indian talent. Asia Lions represent the cricketing powerhouses of Asia. And, a fiery blend of international talent makes up the team of World Giants. 

It has also presented the franchise-based edition of Legends League Cricket, which is held in India. Four privately owned teams compete in this exciting tournament: India Capitals, Gujarat Giants, Bhilwara Kings, and Manipal Tiger. India Capitals team is owned by GMR Sportsline, which also co-owns the IPL team Delhi Capitals. Gujarat Giants team is owned by Adani Sportline, which also owns Gujarat Giants team in the Women's Premier League (WPL). Bhilwara Kings is owned by The LNJ Bhilwara Group. Manipal Tigers is owned by Manipal Education and Medical Group. Two new teams joined the second season, Urbanrisers Hyderabad which is owned by the prestigious Urbanrise Group in collaboration with Mr. JC Pavan Reddy, and Southern Super Stars which is owned by KLO Sports with Ranjeeth Rathod.

Absolute Legends Sports Pvt. Ltd. is the owner and operator of Legends League Cricket. It aspires to create a cricket community where legendary players from around the world come once again to compete and inspire. 

The Upcoming season of Legends League Cricket will be held in India from November to December. Legends League Cricket reinvents passion for cricket, sportsmanship, and competition. Let’s celebrate the spirit of cricket together.

know more : https://www.llct20.com/
Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/llct20
Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/llct20/
Twitter : https://twitter.com/llct20

Legends League Cricket is dedicated to cricket lovers and is a pioneer in offering a platform where retired cricket players can demonstrate their skills, engage with fans, and sense the thrill of cricket once again. The league is dedicated to bring cricket enthusiasts from all walks of life together to celebrate this exciting sport. 

At Legends League Cricket, there are two distinctive cricketing formats being played: Regional and Franchise. Each format gives the game its own charm and competitiveness, providing players and fans with a combination of exciting encounters. 

Legends League Cricket introduced its global format, LLC Masters in 2022 in an effort to push the limits of cricketing excellence. Its inaugural season was hosted by Muscat, Oman, and the most recent season was hosted by Doha, Qatar. The three teams that compete in this format to showcase the best of talent: Indian Maharajas, Asia Lions, and World Giants. Representing the nation’s cricket-crazy culture, India Maharajas bring together the best Indian talent. Asia Lions represent the cricketing powerhouses of Asia. And, a fiery blend of international talent makes up the team of World Giants. 

It has also presented the franchise-based edition of Legends League Cricket, which is held in India. Four privately owned teams compete in this exciting tournament: India Capitals, Gujarat Giants, Bhilwara Kings, and Manipal Tiger. India Capitals team is owned by GMR Sportsline, which also co-owns the IPL team Delhi Capitals. Gujarat Giants team is owned by Adani Sportline, which also owns Gujarat Giants team in the Women's Premier League (WPL). Bhilwara Kings is owned by The LNJ Bhilwara Group. Manipal Tigers is owned by Manipal Education and Medical Group. Two new teams joined the second season, Urbanrisers Hyderabad which is owned by the prestigious Urbanrise Group in collaboration with Mr. JC Pavan Reddy, and Southern Super Stars which is owned by KLO Sports with Ranjeeth Rathod.

Absolute Legends Sports Pvt. Ltd. is the owner and operator of Legends League Cricket. It aspires to create a cricket community where legendary players from around the world come once again to compete and inspire. 

The Upcoming season of Legends League Cricket will be held in India from November to December. Legends League Cricket reinvents passion for cricket, sportsmanship, and competition. Let’s celebrate the spirit of cricket together.

snippet.title: FilterCopy | Falling In Love After Arranged Marriage | Ft. Anshuman Malhotra,  Esha Kansara
snippet.description:
From arranged marriage to happily ever after, we found love ❤️

Approximately 12 million in India are living with epilepsy* - a neurological condition. It is surrounded by social stigma and taboos that emanate due to lack of correct information. 

Sanofi (India) wants to change that!

This film helps bust many common myths about epilepsy, so the right information can help spread awareness. Watch it to rid yourself of any misconceptions about epilepsy!  Like and share it with your network, so you help educate others, too. 

This can be your pledge to spread the word about what's right. 
To know more on epilepsy and how it can be managed, visit: http://surl.sanofi.com/daretoknowepilepsy

*Reference - Epilepsy in India I: Epidemiology and public health - PMC (nih.gov), available at https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4564458/

Subscribe Karein Humare 2nd YouTube Channel ko:
▶𝐌𝐚𝐚 𝐘𝐞𝐡 𝐊𝐚𝐢𝐬𝐞 𝐊𝐚𝐫𝐮𝐧?: https://www.youtube.com/c/Maayehkaisekarun
🌐𝐖𝐞𝐛𝐬𝐢𝐭𝐞 𝐋𝐢𝐧𝐤 - https://www.poonamdevnani.com/
------------------------------------
👉𝐑𝐄𝐋𝐀𝐓𝐄𝐃 𝐋𝐈𝐍𝐊𝐒:
Healthy Nasta - Recipe
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gzpzHHmuzUI

7 Days Zero Oil Thali - Recipe
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w26caCdKze8&t=1s

5 Day Lunch Box Recipes - Recipe
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W6nmDisLUDI

Easy & Healthy Veg Soup - Recipe
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JRIjAeLvn1s

Street Style Momos - Recipe
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=keexgP__LhU
---------------------------------------
✍🏻𝐑𝐄𝐂𝐈𝐏𝐄:
𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐀𝐦𝐥𝐚 𝐂𝐡𝐮𝐭𝐧𝐞𝐲, wash the Gooseberry/Amla & grate it. Keep the pan on the flame, and put some Ghee, Fennel Seeds, Cumin Seeds, Green Cardamom, grated Gooseberry/Amla, Jaggery, and Sugar. Mix well & cook on a high flame. Add Balck Salt, Rock Salt, Coriander Powder, Red Chili Powder, Kashmiri Red Chili Powder, Chat Masala and roasted Cumin Powder. Mix well & cook it till it gets dry. Then Add some Dried Ginger Powder and Melon Seeds. Then keep it for cooling down. 
𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐌𝐮𝐫𝐚𝐛𝐛𝐚, soak Gooseberries overnight. Wipe them and prick them with the fork. Boil Water and add Amla. Cover and cook for 5-7 minutes. In a pan add Candy Sugar/Mishri, pricked & boiled Gooseberries/Amla, and Water. Stir it continuously, cover it, and cook on a slow flame for 40-45 minutes. When the Amla color changed & Syrup turned thicker then put the flame off and take it out. Add Cardamom Powder, Black Salt, and Dry Ginger Powder and mix it well.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Baylagaam Mega Episode 44 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Abbas - Laiba Khan - Haroon Shahid - Tuba Anwar - 19th  November 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

The story centers around Ramsha, a young girl and the only child of her loving parents, Sajid and Mehnaz. Raised with affection and no restrictions, Ramsha enjoys unlimited internet access, which leads to her spending an excessive time on social media, quickly becoming her hobby.
As her fascination with social media intensifies, Ramsha's hobby evolves into an all-consuming passion for fame, prompting her to take extreme measures. During her relentless pursuit of stardom, she crosses paths with Afnan, the son of the influential businessman Qasim Ali. While Afnan, who holds affection for his paternal cousin Aleezay, views Ramsha as a source of amusement, she misinterprets their friendship as love.
Disheartened by her failed search for love, Ramsha turns towards fame. Ramsha's unwavering quest for popularity propels her onto a challenging path, causing turmoil within her family. As her popularity soars, she becomes increasingly distant from her loved ones, leading her life down a tumultuous road, where she discovers the other side of fame many people are unaware of. Along this journey, she encounters Afnan once more, but circumstances have taken a different turn.
Will Ramsha achieve the fame she so desperately desires? Will her pursuit bring dire consequences? Can she find contentment in fame instead of love? And will Ramsha's parents have to bear the consequences of her passion?

snippet.title: Yo Yo Honey Singh on Love, Heartbreak, Betrayal | Honey Singh Podcast | Sadhika Sehgal | MLR Ep 32
snippet.description:
Today we are in conversation with the much-awaited guest, none other than the G.O.A.T., Yo Yo Honey Singh! 

Known for laying the foundations of the OG gang, Mafia Mundeer, that gave a different hype to the Indian rap industry, Honey Singh has successfully dominated the music scene with his catchy tunes and energetic performances, on and off-screen.

As we unpack the numerous layers to his personal and professional journey in this episode with Sadhika Sehgal, we are spilling the tea on everything—from his wildest dreams to the secret sauce that keeps him at the top of the game. And yes, we're even dishing on that epic meet-up with the legend himself, AR Rahman.

From his latest songs to his upcoming documentary on Netflix, catch the ‘Angreji Beat’ fame share his thoughts on rising to fame and the fallback he experienced. 

Ever wondered what life means to Yo Yo Honey Singh? Or why do his fans adore him so much? We're getting real on all that and more—how he handles the haters, the times he's been misunderstood, and his advice for non-believers in God and the astrological realm.

We're taking you behind the scenes of his life, exploring the lessons he learned from the tough times, his fearless attitude, and, of course, the lowdown on love and heartbreak. Ishq versus pyaar, his school gang stories, thoughts on karma—you name it, we're chatting about it.

Curious about his take on male friendships and what "mardangi" (masculinity) means to him? We've got the deets. Plus, we're delving into his unconventional career advice for those who can't stand the 9-to-5 grind, and the real talk on toxic traits.

Buckle up for the ride as we spill the tea on his concert moments, including that one time he got a little heated, and yes, even his mom giving him an earful.

Don't forget to watch an exclusive peek into the life and mind of Yo Yo Honey Singh, showcasing his emotional side for the very first time on the big screen!  To know more about our Desi Kalaakar watch the full episode and get ready for all the feels!

Known for laying the foundations of the OG gang, Mafia Mundeer, that gave a different hype to the Indian rap industry, Honey Singh has successfully dominated the music scene with his catchy tunes and energetic performances, on and off-screen.

As we unpack the numerous layers to his personal and professional journey in this episode with Sadhika Sehgal, we are spilling the tea on everything—from his wildest dreams to the secret sauce that keeps him at the top of the game. And yes, we're even dishing on that epic meet-up with the legend himself, AR Rahman.

From his latest songs to his upcoming documentary on Netflix, catch the ‘Angreji Beat’ fame share his thoughts on rising to fame and the fallback he experienced. 

Ever wondered what life means to Yo Yo Honey Singh? Or why do his fans adore him so much? We're getting real on all that and more—how he handles the haters, the times he's been misunderstood, and his advice for non-believers in God and the astrological realm.

We're taking you behind the scenes of his life, exploring the lessons he learned from the tough times, his fearless attitude, and, of course, the lowdown on love and heartbreak. Ishq versus pyaar, his school gang stories, thoughts on karma—you name it, we're chatting about it.

Curious about his take on male friendships and what "mardangi" (masculinity) means to him? We've got the deets. Plus, we're delving into his unconventional career advice for those who can't stand the 9-to-5 grind, and the real talk on toxic traits.

Buckle up for the ride as we spill the tea on his concert moments, including that one time he got a little heated, and yes, even his mom giving him an earful.

Don't forget to watch an exclusive peek into the life and mind of Yo Yo Honey Singh, showcasing his emotional side for the very first time on the big screen!  To know more about our Desi Kalaakar watch the full episode and get ready for all the feels!

Welcome to our channel, where we delve into the intriguing world of cricket controversies! In this video, we explore the recent claims made by Pakistani players, shedding light on their allegations against India's victories in World Cup matches. From ball tampering to DRS manipulation and even accusations of cheating in the toss, the cricketing rivalry between India and Pakistan takes a new turn.

Hasan Raza, a former Pakistani cricketer, ignited the fire by suggesting that the Board of Control for Cricket in India (BCCI) is providing different balls to Indian bowlers, giving them an unfair advantage in swinging conditions. The plot thickens as we dissect this claim and examine the evidence, separating fact from fiction.

But the drama doesn't end there. Some Pakistani players have raised eyebrows about the Decision Review System (DRS), alleging that India has found a way to manipulate the system in their favor. Join us as we analyze these allegations, exploring the intricacies of the DRS and whether there's any truth to the accusations.

Sikander Bakht's recent statement about India allegedly cheating in the toss adds another layer to the controversy. We break down the claims, providing context and examining the impact of the toss on match outcomes. Is there a strategic advantage at play, or are these allegations merely a product of rivalry and competition?

To offer a balanced perspective, we delve into the history of cross-border cricketing banter. Inzamam ul Haq's revelation about the Pakistani team attempting to convert Harbhajan Singh to Islam adds an interesting twist. Additionally, we feature Javed Miandad's controversial statements about Ram Mandir, providing insights into the complex relationship between cricket and socio-political narratives.

As we present this comprehensive exploration, it's essential to consider whether these claims are rooted in genuine concerns or if they're fueled by the age-old rivalry between India and Pakistan. Are these allegations a reflection of healthy competition or mere jealousy of India's success on the cricketing stage?

Join the conversation in the comments section below and share your thoughts on these controversies. Remember to like, share, and subscribe for more intriguing insights into the world of cricket!

snippet.title: Kadavul Paadhi Mirugam Paadhi Lyric Video | Aalavandhan | Kamal Haasan | Suresh Krissna | SEL
snippet.description:
Dive into the enigmatic depths of Nandhu through the visual poetry Kadavul Paadhi Mirugam Paadhi from Aalavandhan, a song that artfully narrates Nandhu's internal struggles. This track is not just music to the ears but a metaphorical exploration of the perennial battle between good and evil within a single soul.

snippet.title: The most Interesting festival of Uttarakhand | EP02 - Melodies of India
snippet.description:
Join our Storytelling MasterClass for Youtube : https://monkeymagic.wtf/
Use Coupon code : DIWALIMAGIC to get additional 20% off 

Pre-Book your book of Melodies : (currently pre booking is unavailable, we are working on it to bring it live soon) 

Watch Episode 01 : https://youtu.be/9xGlf83nd1Q 
Watch all episodes here : https://shorturl.at/bez02

==========================================================
Instagram : 
Monkey Magic : https://www.instagram.com/monkeyxmagic/
Homestay : https://www.instagram.com/bhagirathi_homestay_bagori/
==========================================================

पाण्डव नृत्य | Episode 02 - Melodies of India 

While walking from Gangotri, following the river Ganga I came across this beautiful little village called Bagori in Harshil, Uttarakhand. 
To my pure luck I was at the right time at the right place as I got to witness the most famous festival of Uttarakhand, that is पाण्डव नृत्य  

Pandav dance is a folk dance of Uttarakhand. This dance is related to the lives of the five Pandavas of the Mahabharata period. Pandavas and Draupadi are worshiped through this dance

This festival takes place every year on the sixth day of Navratri

==========================================================

Heading onto a new journey, that's shape me inside out :) 

What is Melodies of India? 

Magic Monkey, a new age travel YouTube channel travelled and explored by Raunaq Sahni is thrilled to announce an extraordinary and ambitious project. In the quest to unravel the soul of India, Raunaq embarks on a six-month odyssey across the country, meticulously documenting the essence of what it truly means to be Indian. 

The "Melodies of India" project as envisioned by Raunaq is an expedition that aims to capture the heart and spirit of India, transcending its deep-rooted cultures into a visually captivating series of photographs and videos, each narrating a unique facet of our incredible nation. These photographs and videos will serve as visual testimonies, encapsulating the diversity, traditions, and modernisation of India. 

He will later publish 11 photographs along with the moving stories in a Photobook.

==========================================================

पाण्डव नृत्य | Episode 02 - Melodies of India 

While walking from Gangotri, following the river Ganga I came across this beautiful little village called Bagori in Harshil, Uttarakhand. 
To my pure luck I was at the right time at the right place as I got to witness the most famous festival of Uttarakhand, that is पाण्डव नृत्य  

Pandav dance is a folk dance of Uttarakhand. This dance is related to the lives of the five Pandavas of the Mahabharata period. Pandavas and Draupadi are worshiped through this dance

This festival takes place every year on the sixth day of Navratri

==========================================================

Heading onto a new journey, that's shape me inside out :) 

What is Melodies of India? 

Magic Monkey, a new age travel YouTube channel travelled and explored by Raunaq Sahni is thrilled to announce an extraordinary and ambitious project. In the quest to unravel the soul of India, Raunaq embarks on a six-month odyssey across the country, meticulously documenting the essence of what it truly means to be Indian. 

The "Melodies of India" project as envisioned by Raunaq is an expedition that aims to capture the heart and spirit of India, transcending its deep-rooted cultures into a visually captivating series of photographs and videos, each narrating a unique facet of our incredible nation. These photographs and videos will serve as visual testimonies, encapsulating the diversity, traditions, and modernisation of India. 

He will later publish 11 photographs along with the moving stories in a Photobook.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Baylagaam Mega Episode 43 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Abbas - Laiba Khan - Haroon Shahid - Tuba Anwar - 19th  November 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

The story centers around Ramsha, a young girl and the only child of her loving parents, Sajid and Mehnaz. Raised with affection and no restrictions, Ramsha enjoys unlimited internet access, which leads to her spending an excessive time on social media, quickly becoming her hobby.
As her fascination with social media intensifies, Ramsha's hobby evolves into an all-consuming passion for fame, prompting her to take extreme measures. During her relentless pursuit of stardom, she crosses paths with Afnan, the son of the influential businessman Qasim Ali. While Afnan, who holds affection for his paternal cousin Aleezay, views Ramsha as a source of amusement, she misinterprets their friendship as love.
Disheartened by her failed search for love, Ramsha turns towards fame. Ramsha's unwavering quest for popularity propels her onto a challenging path, causing turmoil within her family. As her popularity soars, she becomes increasingly distant from her loved ones, leading her life down a tumultuous road, where she discovers the other side of fame many people are unaware of. Along this journey, she encounters Afnan once more, but circumstances have taken a different turn.
Will Ramsha achieve the fame she so desperately desires? Will her pursuit bring dire consequences? Can she find contentment in fame instead of love? And will Ramsha's parents have to bear the consequences of her passion?

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3931 | 17 Nov 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3931: Jethalal Gets Impatient
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha urgently phones all of Sundar's phone numbers, but he is never able to contact him. Jetha is relieved when an uncle who is Daya's neighbor answers the phone. Jetha asks the elderly guy to connect him with Daya. The old guy pays a visit to Daya's home, but he informs Jetha that she is not there. Sundar even ignores Tapu's call. Why did Sundar not answer his phone?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3931, 17 Nov 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
